Byte-by-byte Description of file: states.dat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format Units           Label   Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1- 3   I3    ---             index   index
   4- 14  A11   ---             label   term label
  15- 18  I4    ---             g       statistical weight
  19- 25  F7.3   eV             E       term energy in eV  			  
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Byte-by-byte Description of file: *_b.dat and *_c.dat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format    Units  Label         Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1-250  25E10.2   ---   Upsilon       Effective collision strengths matrix (1)   
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note (1): The matrices follow the ordering of indexes in states.data; i.e. the 
   transition 1-2 corresponds to element (1,2), noting the matrix is symmetric.
